<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="644" />The men were in fine health and <unclear /> the promise of adventure <unclear /> ahead given by the presence <unclear /> <persName n="Stuart,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00242" reg="mostcommon:Stuart,nomatch:0" authname="stuart"><roleName n="General" full="yes">Gen.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Stuart</surname></persName>, who was to lead <unclear />. The men sprang to the saddle with <unclear /> marched off at the word of <unclear>com</unclear> as a band of fort-<unclear>hufiters,</unclear> out <unclear /> run, at the sound of <q direct="unspecified">"tally-ho."</q> <unclear /> the right of the enemy's line, <unclear /> occurred to break in upon the <unclear /> diversion in the route was <unclear>cre</unclear> enemy.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="645" />The <num value="1" type="ordinal">first</num> day's tramp led <unclear /> <placeName reg="Taylorsville, Hanover, Virginia" key="tgn,2114568" authname="tgn,2114568">Taylorsville</placeName>, in <placeName reg="Hanover, Hanover, Virginia" key="tgn,2112147" authname="tgn,2112147">Hanover</placeName>, where <unclear /> picketed and the men <unclear>bi</unclear> the night.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="646" />During the night <unclear /> was vigilant, and kept out a sufficient of scouts and videttes to prevent <unclear /> were now within the enemy's <unclear /> the rear of the <q direct="unspecified">"Grand Army,"</q> as <unclear /> are fond of calling it — probably <unclear />principle, because <unclear /> about it. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="647" /> <unclear /> morning, before the <num value="1" type="ordinal">first</num> red light appeared along the horizon, <unclear /> sounded, and the men were again <unclear /> going in the direction of <placeName reg="Hanover, Hanover, Virginia" key="tgn,2112147" authname="tgn,2112147">Hanover</placeName> <unclear /> the <num value="1" type="ordinal">first</num> difficulties of this perilous <unclear /> Some <num value="75">seventy-five</num> or a <num value="100">hundred</num> <unclear /> in <placeName reg="Hanover, Hanover, Virginia" key="tgn,2112147" authname="tgn,2112147">Hanover</placeName> fled at their <unclear>ap </unclear> were soon lost in the distance.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="648" />At <unclear /> <placeName reg="Hawes's Shop">Hawes's Shop</placeName> our advance <unclear>re </unclear> <orgName n="Dragoons Company" type="company">company of dragoons</orgName> drawn up in <unclear /> <persName n="Stuart,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00243" reg="mostcommon:Stuart,nomatch:0" authname="stuart"><surname full="yes">Stuart</surname></persName> ordered a squadron to charge, <unclear /> sabres and in column of fours.

