<milestone unit="sentence" n="667" /><persName n="Lee,Colonel,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00252" reg="nearbymention:Lee,Fitz,Hugh,," authname="lee,fitz,hugh"><roleName n="Colonel" full="yes">Col.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Lee</surname></persName>, of the <num value="9" type="ordinal">9th</num> <unclear /> Cavalry, plunged into the rapid <unclear /> and, at great peril, swam across.--<unclear /> return he reported that he <unclear /> it impracticable to cross with <unclear /> and artillery.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="668" />Here was a <unclear>dilem </unclear> enemy having received information <unclear /> the affair, would undoubtedly send out <unclear /> force to make an attack.

