<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="830" /> On <dateStruct value="--16" full="yes" authname="---16"><day type="name" full="yes">Monday</day>, <day reg="16" full="yes">16th instant</day></dateStruct>, <persName n="Allen,,Lucy,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00319" reg="default:Allen,Lucy,,," authname="allen,lucy"><foreName full="yes">Lucy</foreName> <surname full="yes">Allen</surname></persName>, only child of <rs type="role2">Major</rs> S. P. and <persName n="Mitchell,,Mary,E.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00320" reg="default:Mitchell,Mary,E.,," authname="mitchell,mary,e."><foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName> <foreName full="yes">E.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Mitchell</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="13months" type="date">13 months</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="831" /> The funeral will take place on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Wednesday</day></dateStruct>, at <time value="10am">10 o'clock A. M.</time>, from <placeName reg="St. Paul's Church">St. Paul's Church</placeName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="832" />The friends of the family are invited to attend without further notice. 2t </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
