<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1009" /> <hi rend="bold">all members of Sapper and Miner Company,</hi> now absent without leave, are hereby notified to return to their camp at <placeName reg="Drury's Bluff">Drury's Bluff</placeName>, <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">James River</placeName>, immediately, or they will be published and treated as deserters.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1010" />Persons members of other companies yet in the service of the <placeName reg="United States" key="tgn,7012149" authname="tgn,7012149">Confederate States</placeName>, who have been induced to join this company through misrepresentations, and who have returned to their old companies without reporting here, will please procure a certificate to that effect from their commanding officer, and forward same to me, and by so doing avoid having their names published as deserters. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Boylan,,Frank,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00454" reg="default:Boylan,Frank,,," authname="boylan,frank"><foreName full="yes">Frank</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Boylan</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> je <num value="16">16</num>--2t* <rs type="role" reg="Lieutenant-1">1st Lieut</rs>, Comd'g <orgName type="company" n="Company S">Co. S</orgName>. and M. </closer> </div3> 
