<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1044" /> The attention of recruiting officers is particularly called to the above advertisement, as it is suspected these men will re-enlist for the benefit of the bounty as often as they can do so. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Taylor,,A.,S.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00483" reg="default:Taylor,A.,S.,," authname="taylor,a.,s."><foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">S.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Taylor</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> je <num value="11">11</num>--6t <rs type="role2">Major</rs> and Quar'r, C. S. M. C. <lb /> <orgName n="Petersburg Express" type="newspaper">Petersburg Express</orgName> copy for <num value="1">one</num> week, and send bill to this Department. </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="7" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>City Battalion.--<lb /><persName n="Elliott,Major,W.,M.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00484" reg="default:Elliott,W.,M.,," authname="elliott,w.,m."><roleName n="Major" full="yes">Maj.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">M.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Elliott</surname></persName>, Commanding.<lb />pay <measure n="31dollars" type="currency">$31</measure> per month and rations.</head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1045" /> <num value="100">one hundred</num> men Wanted, between the ages of <num value="16">16</num> and <num value="45">45</num>, for a company in the above Battalion for local and special defence of the city of <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName> or <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Manchester</placeName>, for a term of <measure n="6months" type="date">six months</measure>, unless sooner discharged by order of the <rs type="role" reg="Secretary of War">Secretary of War</rs>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1046" /> None but men of good character will be received.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1047" />Apply, between the hours of <time value="9am">9 A. M.</time> and <time value="2pm">2 P. M.</time> to </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Harrison,,W.,W.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00485" reg="default:Harrison,W.,W.,," authname="harrison,w.,w."><foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">W.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Harrison</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> At <persName n="Ragland,,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00486" reg="mostcommon:Ragland,nomatch:0" authname="ragland"><surname full="yes">Ragland</surname></persName> &amp; Bro.'s, cor. <num value="9" type="ordinal">9th</num> and Main sts; <lb /> <signed><persName n="Baughman,,George,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00487" reg="default:Baughman,George,,," authname="baughman,george"><foreName n="George" full="yes">Geo.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Baughman</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <signed><persName n="Allison,,W.,H.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00488" reg="default:Allison,W.,H.,," authname="allison,w.,h."><foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Allison</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <address><street n="Main Street 221">221 Main street</street></address>; <lb /> <signed><persName n="West,,John,M.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00489" reg="default:West,John,M.,," authname="west,john,m."><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">M.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">West</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> je <num value="11">11</num>--12t* <address><street n="Main Street 145">145 Main street</street></address>. </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="8" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Hdq'rs <orgName type="mil" key="MDPartisanCorps">Md. Partisan Corps</orgName>,<lb /><hi rend="smallcaps"><placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>,</hi> <date value="1862-05-28" authname="1862-05-28">may 28, 1862.</date></head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1048" /> the undersigned having received authority to organize a <orgName type="mil" key="PartisanCorps">Partisan Corps</orgName> of Marylanders, invites all young men from that State to join his corps, which will be composed of cavalry, artillery and infantry. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1049" /> Horses will be furnished to the cavalry, if requested.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1050" />Pay, rations and bounty the same as in regular service, and the value of all captures divided in the corps. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1051" /> Marylanders enlisted for <measure n="12months" type="date">12 months</measure>, including those who have re-enlisted, can obtain transfers to this corps. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1052" /> <placeName reg="Recruiting office">Recruiting office</placeName> at <persName n="Weston,Major,J.,A.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00490" reg="default:Weston,J.,A.,," authname="weston,j.,a."><roleName n="Major" full="yes">Maj.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Weston</surname></persName>'s Counting Room.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1053" /><address><street n="Pearl Street 15">No. 15 Pearl street</street></address>. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Jenifer,,W.,H.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00491" reg="default:Jenifer,W.,H.,," authname="jenifer,w.,h."><foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Jenifer</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> my <num value="29">29</num>--ts <rs type="role2">Colonel</rs> P. A. C. S. </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="9" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak">Attention, <orgName n="Artillery"><persName n="Martin,,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00492" reg="nearbymention:Martin,T.,Edward,," authname="martin,t.,edward"><surname full="yes">Martin</surname></persName>'s Artillery</orgName>!</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1054" /> --All members of this command who are absent without leave, will report at once to <placeName reg="Camp Lee">Camp Lee</placeName>, or they will be reported to the <orgName n="Provost Guard" type="guard">Provost Guard</orgName> and arrested as deserters. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1055" /> Persons wishing to join the company will apply to Serg't <persName n="Pulliam,,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00493" reg="mostcommon:Pulliam,nomatch:0" authname="pulliam"><surname full="yes">Pulliam</surname></persName>, at the recruiting office, corner of <address><street n="Bank Street">Bank</street></address> and <address><street n="12 Street">12th streets</street></address>. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Martin,,S.,Taylor,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00494" reg="default:Martin,S.,Taylor,," authname="martin,s.,taylor"><foreName full="yes">S.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">Taylor</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Martin</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> ap <num value="81">81</num>--ts <rs type="role2">Captain</rs>. </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="10" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><orgName n="Ordnance Department" type="department">Ordnance Department of <placeName reg="Virginia" key="tgn,7007919" authname="tgn,7007919">Va.</placeName></orgName>,<lb /><hi rend="smallcaps"><placeName reg="Lynchburg, Lynchburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7013981" authname="tgn,7013981">Lynchburg</placeName>,</hi> <date value="1862-06-12" authname="1862-06-12">June 12, 1862.</date></head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1056" /> notice.--As all preparations for <orgName n="Army"><persName n="Floyd,Major-General,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00495" reg="mostcommon:Floyd,nomatch:0" authname="floyd"><roleName n="Major-General" full="yes">Major General</roleName> <surname full="yes">Floyd</surname></persName>'s Army</orgName> are being concentrated at <placeName reg="Lynchburg, Lynchburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7013981" authname="tgn,7013981">Lynchburg</placeName>, the issues from this Department will be there made. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1057" /> Requisitions must be <num value="1" type="ordinal">first</num> signed by <persName n="Floyd,General,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00496" reg="mostcommon:Floyd,nomatch:0" authname="floyd"><roleName n="General" full="yes">Gen.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Floyd</surname></persName> or some officer authorized by him, then approved by <persName n="Richardson,Adjutant General,William,H.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00497" reg="default:Richardson,William,H.,," authname="richardson,william,h."><roleName n="Adjutant General" full="yes">Adjutant-General</roleName> <foreName n="William" full="yes">Wm.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Richardson</surname></persName>, at <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>, upon which the issues will be made. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Dimmock,,C.,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00498" reg="default:Dimmock,C.,,," authname="dimmock,c."><foreName full="yes">C.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Dimmock</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> je <num value="12">12</num>--ts <rs type="role" reg="Brigadier-General">Brig. Gen.</rs> Ordnance of Va. <lb /> Enquirer and Whig will copy. </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="11" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><placeName reg="Camp Thomas Artillery">Camp Thomas Artillery</placeName>,<hi rend="smallcaps">near <placeName reg="Blakey's Mill Pond">Blakey's Mill Pond</placeName>,</hi><date value="1862-06-12" authname="1862-06-12">June 12, 1862.</date></head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1058" /> <measure n="30dollars" type="currency">30 Dollars</measure> reward will be paid for the arrest and confinement or delivery in camp of the following named deserters: </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1059" /> <persName n="Cummings,,John,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00499" reg="default:Cummings,John,,," authname="cummings,john"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <surname full="yes">Cummings</surname></persName>, <persName n="Cook,,Joseph,M.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00500" reg="default:Cook,Joseph,M.,," authname="cook,joseph,m."><foreName n="Joseph" full="yes">Jos.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">M.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Cook</surname></persName>, <persName n="Doherty,,Matthew,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00501" reg="default:Doherty,Matthew,,," authname="doherty,matthew"><foreName full="yes">Matthew</foreName> <surname full="yes">Doherty</surname></persName>, <persName n="Harris,,Marcellus,W.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00502" reg="default:Harris,Marcellus,W.,," authname="harris,marcellus,w."><foreName full="yes">Marcellus</foreName> <foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Harris</surname></persName>, <persName n="Hutchinson,,William,P.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00503" reg="default:Hutchinson,William,P.,," authname="hutchinson,william,p."><foreName n="William" full="yes">Wm.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">P.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Hutchinson</surname></persName>, <persName n="Smith,,Thomas,J.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00504" reg="default:Smith,Thomas,J.,," authname="smith,thomas,j."><foreName n="Thomas" full="yes">Thos.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Smith</surname></persName>, <persName n="Roane,,Patrick,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00505" reg="default:Roane,Patrick,,," authname="roane,patrick"><foreName full="yes">Patrick</foreName> <surname full="yes">Roane</surname></persName> <hi rend="italics">alias</hi> <persName n="Melton,,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00506" reg="mostcommon:Melton,nomatch:0" authname="melton"><surname full="yes">Melton</surname></persName>. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Anderson,,E.,J.,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00507" reg="default:Anderson,E.,J.,," authname="anderson,e.,j."><foreName full="yes">E.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Anderson</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> je <num value="13">13</num>--6t* <persName n="Comd,Captain,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00508" reg="mostcommon:Comd,nomatch:0" authname="comd"><roleName n="Captain" full="yes">Capt.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Comd</surname></persName>'g Battery. </closer> </div3> 
