<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1061" /> Wanted — Recruits for the <name>Floyd</name> <orgName n="Light Artillery" type="artillery">light Artillery</orgName>, to serve for <measure n="12months" type="date">twelve months</measure>. A fine field battery has been secured. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1062" /> Uniforms, Board, and Equipments furnished, and pay from date of enlistment. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1063" /> Apply at <num value="2">No. 2</num> <placeName reg="Law Building">Law Building</placeName>, <address><street n="Franklin street">Franklin</street></address>, between <address><street n="12 Street">12th</street></address> and <address><street n="13 Street">13th streets</street></address>. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Fontaine,,W.,Winston,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00510" reg="default:Fontaine,W.,Winston,," authname="fontaine,w.,winston"><foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">Winston</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Fontaine</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> je <num value="13">13</num>--12t* <orgName type="mil" key="LightArtillery"><persName n="Floyd,Captain,,,," id="n-0001.0001.00000.00511" reg="mostcommon:Floyd,nomatch:0" authname="floyd"><roleName n="Captain" full="yes">Capt.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Floyd</surname></persName> Light Artillery</orgName>. </closer> </div3> 
